<p>But what if the element's CSS is like the following?</p>

<pre><code>.element{
    position: absolute;left:-9999;    
}
</code></pre>

<p>So <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/8897289">this answer to Stack Overflow question <em>How to check if an element is off-screen</em></a> should also be considered.</p>
